N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 22 ยง 129.5 - Liability

State Regulations

Nothing in this Part shall be construed as
creating a cause of action for damages or injunctive relief against the State
or any of its political subdivisions or officers or any agency
thereof. Notes
